data.description: Here is your chance to own in Barnegat township. This home has been completely redone. A new septic was installed April 2023. This home has Two bedrooms on the main floor. and a full bath, The home has a basement with full bathroom and office space along with an area for a great family or Tv room. The attic can  accommodate so many options for living space.  All new appliances and flooring throughout the home. Don't let your opportunity to own your own home . Come see this gem today.
